reviewText:
Why is Dimmu Borgir not on this DVD when it's advertised and playing on YouTube?
I ordered this on DVD back in 2012.
The Wacken concerts are usually pretty good so I purchased this one an a couple more.
All and any wacken germany metal festival dvds are top of the line, bands galore and great footage and sound are standard for wacken dvds u get 2 to three discs.
